Package stacks

Class Navigator

java.lang.Object
stacks.Navigator
public class Navigator extends Object
An object of type Navigator helps to keep track of two StackList objects as well as a currentLink to see where the user is in a set of instructions
Author:
Foothill College, Jason Palmeri
